{"tid":247073,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]希比落淚: 我唔係叫春既女人😞","createTime":"2017-05-17T13:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T10:39:24.000Z","uid":35341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7112048d8f2972e78eebdc745e1837ff1bc50a5","tid":247073,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:31:04.000Z","msg":"今晚9時許，希比到連登如常開post，趕看帖子《阿仙奴球迷16-17吹水區xxxxxx》。開頭急急腳走Lihkg上架crew車度，跟住落番嚟接受訪問，行埋一邊，回應傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n「首先我想講就係，我只係一個生日嘅聚會上我見到鼻祖(Joe)，嗰張相喺一個annual dinner裏面，佢叫我幫佢影獨照，同佢唔係話真係好熟，張相嘅由來，就唔再諗。點解要講到我係一個叫春嘅女人？我唔係叫春嘅女人，以前唔係，今日唔係，以後都唔係！」希又稱在那個moment，「我係完全唔係佢，佢只係一個普通嘅朋友。」<br />\n<br />\n「上黎入咗十幾星期，想畀啲行動證明畀大家睇開post，畀啲成績大家睇，但估唔到傳呢啲咁嘅嘢出嚟。」中段希比忍不住落淚，更一度說不下去，垂頭沉吟良久。"},{"pid":"41cc4438fd8c63c91d7397837bc7801e5b1a4e50","tid":247073,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:31:36.000Z","msg":"食屎啦鼻祖"},{"pid":"ab913587d0967895677db9e5b6ef3a81945344d0","tid":247073,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食屎啦鼻祖</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb2f4b8c761696f7a28bcc093259a7a1f04f593","tid":247073,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b18bab65216076786709bb3496e5e6ba4783294","tid":247073,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:46:29.000Z","msg":"唔係叫春女人 係叫春狗"},{"pid":"b82d0c3b6a0f31812e2a62fa244f5fa935e71517","tid":247073,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:08:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"